Procedures for installing Apache2
=================================

In this order:

Install openssl from source and install in:
    /opt/openssl-x.y.z.a
    use the local script

Install APR from source in:
    /usr/local   # default
    use the local script

Install APR-UTIL from source in:
    /usr/local   # default
    use the local script

Install apache2 from source and install in:

    use the local script
